### Bot Detection Demo - HTTP Request File
### Use this file with Visual Studio, VS Code REST Client, or JetBrains HTTP Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5080

### ==========================================
### Root & Test Page
### ==========================================

### Get API info (with your current detection status)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api

### ==========================================
### Diagnostic Endpoints
### ==========================================

### Full bot detection check for current request
GET {{baseUrl}}/bot-detection/check

### Get detection statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/bot-detection/stats

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/bot-detection/health

### ==========================================
### Test Mode Simulation (requires EnableTestMode = true)
### ==========================================

### Simulate human visitor
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
ml-bot-test-mode: human

### Simulate Googlebot (Search Engine, Verified)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
ml-bot-test-mode: googlebot

### Simulate Bingbot (Search Engine, Verified)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
ml-bot-test-mode: bingbot

### Simulate Scraper bot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
ml-bot-test-mode: scraper

### Simulate Malicious bot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
ml-bot-test-mode: malicious

### Simulate Social Media bot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
ml-bot-test-mode: social

### Simulate Monitoring bot
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
ml-bot-test-mode: monitor

### Bypass detection entirely
GET {{baseUrl}}/api
ml-bot-test-mode: disable

### ==========================================
### Protected Endpoints
### ==========================================

### Protected endpoint (allows verified bots like Googlebot)
# As human
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/protected
Accept: text/html
Accept-Language: en-US,en
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36

### Protected endpoint - as Googlebot (should be allowed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/protected
ml-bot-test-mode: googlebot

### Protected endpoint - as scraper (should be blocked)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/protected
ml-bot-test-mode: scraper

### Humans-only endpoint (blocks ALL bots including verified)
# As human
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/humans-only
Accept: text/html
Accept-Language: en-US,en
User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36

### Humans-only - as Googlebot (should be blocked)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/humans-only
ml-bot-test-mode: googlebot

### Allow search engines endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/allow-search-engines
ml-bot-test-mode: googlebot

### Allow search engines - as scraper (should be blocked)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/allow-search-engines
ml-bot-test-mode: scraper

### Strict protection (only blocks >90% confidence)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/strict-protection

